hadiths[52]{hadithnumber,text}:
6723,"Abdullah-bin-Numair Hamdani, abu-Muawia aur Wakee ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Zaid-bin Wahab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam), aur wo sach bataatey hain aur unhein (wahi ke zariey se) sach bataya jata hai, ne farmaya : tum mein se har aik shakhs ka maadda takhleeq chalis (40) din tak uski maa ke pet mein ikattha kya jata hai, phir wo itni muddat (chalis (40) din) ke liye alaqa (jonk ki tarah rehem ki diwar ke sath chipka hua) rehta hai, phir itni hi muddat ke liye muzgha ki shakl mein rehta hai (jis mein reedh ki haddi ke nishanat daant se chabai janey ke nishanat se mushabeh (similar) hotey hain.) phir Allah Taala Farishtey ko bhejta hai jo (paanchwein mahiney neuro-cell, yani dimagh ki takhleeq ho janey ke baad) usmein Rooh phoonkta hai. aur usey char baton ka hukm diya jata hai ke iska rizq, uski Umar, iska amal aur ye ke wo khush naseeb hoga ya bad-nasib, likh liya jaey. mujhey us zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi! tum mein se koi aik shakhs ahle-jannat ke se amal karta rehta hai, yahan tak ke jab iske aur jannat ke darmyan aik baalisht ka fasla reh jata hai to (Allah ke ilm ke mutabiq ( likha hua is par ghalib aa jata hai to wo ahale-jahannam ka amal kar leta hai aur us (jahannam) mein dakhil ho jata hai. aur tum mein se aik shakhs ahale-jahannam ke se amal karta rehta hai yahan tak ke iske aur jahannam ke darmyan aik baalisht ka fasla reh jata hai to (Allah ke ilm ke mutabiq) likha hua is par ghalib aa jata hai aur wo ahle-jannat ka amal kar leta hai aur us (jannat) mein dakhil ho jata hai."
6724,"Usman bin abi Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne Jarir bin abdul-hameed se riwayat ki, neez hamein Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne Esa-bin-Yonus se khabar di aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne mujhey bayan kya, kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki ke Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Shoba bin Hajjaj ne hadis bayan ki, un sab ( Jareer, Esa , Wakee aur Shoba ( ne Aamash se, isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki. Wakee ki hadis mein kaha : tum mein se aik insan ka maadda takhleeq chalis (40) raaton tak apni maa ke pet mein ikattha (honey ke marhaley mein) hota hai. aur Shoba se Muaz ki hadis mein chalis (40) raatein ya chalis (40) din aur Jarir aur Esa ki hadis mein chalis (40) din hai."
6725,"Amr-bin-Dinar ne abu-Tufail (Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu)) se, unhon-ne Huzefa bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki jo unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchai (marfooa bayan ki), Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab nutfa (chalis (40) chaalees dinon ke 2 marhalon ke baad teesrey marhaley mein) chalis (40) ya paintaalees raatein rehem mein thehra rehta hai to ( Allah ka muqarrar kya hua) farishta uske paas jata hai aur kehta hai : aey rab! ye khush naseeb hoga ya bad-naseeb hoga? to donon (baton mein se Allah jo bataaey us) ko likh liya jata hai, phir kehta hai : aey rab! ye mard hai ya aurat? phir donon (main se jo Allah bataaey us) ko likh liya jata hai, phir iska amal, iske qadmon ke nishanat, uski muddat umr aur iska rizq likh liya jata hai, phir (indraaj ke) saheefey lapet diye jatey hain, phir unmein koi cheez badhaai jati hai, na kam ki jati hai."
6726,"Amr-bin-Haris ne abu-Zubair Makki se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : bad-bakht wo hai jo apni maa ke pet main (tha to Allah ke ilm ke mutabiq ( bad-bakht tha aur khush-naseebi mand wo hai jo apne ilawa doosrey se nasihat hasil karey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se aik shakhs aaey jinhein Hazrat Huzefa bin Usaid Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha, unhon (Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unko Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke alfaz mein ye hadis sunai aur (unse poochhney ke liye) kaha : wo shakhs koi amal kiye baghair bad-bakht kaisey ho jata hai? to us ( Aamir (Raziallahu anhu)) ko aadmi ( Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : kya aap is par tajjub kartey hain? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai : jab nutfey par (teesrey marhaley ki) bayaalees raatein guzar jati hain to Allah Taala uske paas aik farishta bhejta hai, wo uski sura banata hai, iske kaan , aankhen , khaal , gosht aur uski haddiyaan banata hai, phir kehta hai : aey mere rab! ye mard hoga ke aurat? phir tumhara rab jo chahta hota hai wo faisla bataata hai aur farishta likh leta hai, phir wo kehta hai : aey mere rab! uski muddat hayaat (kitni hogi?) phir tumhara rab jo uski marzi hoti hai, bataata hai aur farishta likh leta hai, phir wo (farishta) kehta hai : aey mere rab! uska rizq (kitna hoga? ( to tumhara rab jo chahta hota hai wo faisla bataata hai aur farishta likh leta hai, phir farishta apne hath mein saheefa lekar nikal jata hai, chunanche wo shakhs kisi mamley mein na us se badhta hai, na kam hota hai."
6727,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they aur Amr-bin-Haris ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6728,"Yahya bin abu-Bukair ne kaha : hamein abu-Khaisma Zuhair ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin Ata ne hadis bayan ki, unhein Ikrima bin Khalid ne hadis bayan ki, unhein abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : main abu Sareeha Huzefa bin Usaid Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir hua to unhon-ne kaha : maine apne un donon kanon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai : nutfa (asl mein teen marhalon mein chalis (40) ( chalis (40) raatein maa k pet mein rehta hai, phir farishta uski sura banata hai. Zuhair ne kaha : mera guman hai ke unhon-ne kaha : ( farishta ( usey banata hai : to wo kehta hai : aey mere rab! aurat hogi ya mard hoga? phir Allah Taala uske muzakkar ya muannas honey ka faisla bata deta hai, wo (farishta) phir kehta hai : aey mere rab! mukammal (poorey aaza wala hai) ya ghair mukammal? phir Allah Taala mukammal ya ghair mukammal honey ke barey mein apna faisla bata deta hai, phir wo kehta hai : aey mere parwardigar ! uska rizq kitna hoga? uski muddate-hayaat kitni hogi ? uska akhlaq kaisa hoga? phir Allah Taala uske bad-bakht ya khush-bakht honey ke barey mein bhi (jo tay ho chuka) bata deta hai."
6729,"kulsoom ne abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi Hazrat Huzefa bin Usaid Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfuan riwayat ki : takhleeq ke doran mein raham par aik farishta muqarrar hota hai, jab Allah Taala apne izn se koi cheez paida karna chahta hai to chalis (40) aur kuchh uper raatein guzarney ke baad phir un sab ki riwayat ki hui hadis ke mutabiq bayan kya."
6730,"Ubaidullah-bin-abi-Bakr ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne ye hadis marfooan bayan ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah raham par aik farishta muqarrar kar deta hai, wo kehta hai : aey mere rab! ( ab) ye nutfa hai, aey mere rab! ( ab ( ye alaqa hai, aey mere rab! ( ab ye muzgha hai, phir jab Allah Taala uski (insan ki sura mein) takhleeq ka faisla karta hai to unhon-ne kaha : farishta kehta hai : aey mere rab! mard ho ya aurat? bad-bakht ho ya khush naseeb? rizq kitna hoga? muddate-Umar kitni hogi? wo maan ke pet mein hota hai aur isi tarah (sab kuchh) likh liya jata hai."
6731,"Jarir ne hamein Mansoor se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sad bin Ubeda se, unhon-ne abu-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham aik janazey ke sath Baqee gharqad mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur baith gaey, ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ird-gird baith gaey. aap ne apna sar Mubarak jhuka liya aur apni chhadi se zamin kuredney lagey (jis tarah ke fikr mandi ke aalim mein hon.) phir farmaya : tum mein se koi aik bhi nahi, koi saans leney wala jaandaar shakhs nahi, magar Allah Taala ne (apne asli hamesha ke aur kabhi na khatm honewale ilm ke mutabiq) jannat ya jahannam mein uska thikana likh diya hai aur (koi nahi) magar (ye bhi) likh diya gaya hai ke wo bad-bakht hai ya khush bakht. kaha : to kisi aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! kya ham apne likhe par hi na reh jayen aur amal chhod dein? to aap ne farmaya : jo khush bakhton mein se hoga to wo khush bakhton ke amal ki taraf chal padega. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : amal karo, har aik ka rasta aasan kar diya gaya hai. jo khush-bakht hain unke liye khush bakhton ke aamaal ka rasta aasan kar diya jata hai aur jo bad-bakht hain unke liye bad-bakhton ke amalon ka rasta aasan kar diya jata hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tilawat kya : to wo shakhs jisne ( Allah ki raah mein) diya aur taqwa ikhtiyar kya aur achi baat ki tasdeeq kar di to ham usey aasani ki zindagi (tak pahunchne) ke liye sahoolat ata karengey aur wo jisne kanjoosi ki aur be parwaai ikhtiyar ki aur achi baat ko jhutlaya to ham usey mushkil zindagi (tak janey) ke liye sahoolat dengey."
6732,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Hannaad bin Sari ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Ahwas ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki aur kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik lakdi pakdi aur chhadi nahi kaha, aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ne abu-Ahwas se bayan ki hui apni hadis mein (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kai jagah) kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tilawat ki."
6733,"Wakee, Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu-Muawia ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Sad-bin-Ubaida se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Abdur-Rehman Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din baithey huey they, aur aap ke hath mein aik chhadi thi jis se aap zamin kured rahe they, phir aap ne apna sare-aqdas utha kar farmaya : tum mein se koi zi-Rooh nahi magar jannat aur dozakh mein iska maqam (pahley se) malum hai. unhon (sahaba) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! phir ham kis liye amal karein? ham usi (likhe huey) par takiya na karein? aap ne farmaya : nahi, tum amal karo, har shakhs ke liye usi ki sahoolat muyassar hai jis (ko khud apne amal ke zariey hasil karne) ke liye usko paida kya gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne : to wo shakhs jisne (Allah ki raah mein) diya aur achi baat ki tasdeeq ki, se lekar to ham usey mushkil zindagi (tak janey) ke liye sahoolat dengey tak padha ."
6734,"hamein Shoba ne Mansoor aur Aamash se hadis bayan ki, un donon ne Sad bin Ubeda se suna, wo abu-Abdur-Rehman Salma se, wo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat kar rahe they."
6735,"abu-Khaisma Zuhair (bin Harab ( ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik bin Jasham (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap hamarey liye Deen ko is tarah bayan kijiye, maano ham abhi paida kiye gaey hain, aaj ka amal (jo ham kar rahe hain) kis naua mein aata hai? kya usmein jisey (likhney wali) qalmein (likh kar) khushk ho chukin aur jo paimaney muqarrar kiye gaey hain unka silsila jari ho chuka hai (ham bas unhi ke mutabiq amal kiye ja rahe hain?) ya usmein jo ham naey sirey se kar rahe hain (pahley se unke barey mein kuchh tay nahi?) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, balke jisey likhney wali qalmein (likh kar) khushk ho chukin aur jinke muqarrar shuda paimaanon ke mutabiq amal shuru ho chuka. unhon-ne kaha : to phir amal kis liye (kya jaaey?) Zuhair ne kaha : phir iske baad abu-Zubair ne koi baat ki jo main nahi samajh saka, to maine puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaaya? unhon-ne kaha : (aap ne farmaya :) tum amal karo, har aik ko sahoolat muyassar ki gaee hai."
6736,"Amr-bin-Haris ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi maana mein riwayat ki aur is mein ye alfaz hain : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har amal karne wala apne amal ke liye aasani paata hai."
6737,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Yazeed Zubai se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Mutarrif ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : Allah ke rasool! kya ye malum hai ke jahannam walon se ( alag ( jannat waley kon hain? kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan. kaha gaya : to phir amal karne waley kis liye amal karein? aap ne farmaya : har aik ko usi (manzil ki taraf janey) ki suhoolat muyassar kar di jati hai jis (tak apne aamaal ke zariey pahunchne) ke liye usey paida kya gaya tha."
6738,"Abdul-Waris, ibne-Ulaih, Jafar bin Sulaiman aur Shoba sab ne Yazeed rashk se isi sanad ke sath Hammad ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki aur Abdul-Waris ki hadis mein (kaha gaya ke bajaey) is tarah hai : ( Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool!"
6739,"Yahya-bin-Yamar ne abu Aswad daili se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : tumhara kya khayal hai ke jo amal log aaj kar rahe hain aur is mein mashaqqat utha rahe hain, kya ye aisi cheez hai jiska unke barey mein faisla ho chuka aur pahley hi se muqaddar hai jo unmein jari ho chuka hai ya wo naey sirey se unke samney pesh ki ja rahi hai, jis tarah usey unke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas laey hain aur un par hujjat qaaim hui hai? maine jawab diya : balke jis tarah unke barey mein faisla ho chuka hai aur uska silsila unmein jari hai. (daili ne) kaha : to (Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to kya ye zulm nahi? (daili ne) kaha : to is baat par main sakht khaufzada aur pareshan ho gaya aur maine kaha : har cheez Allah ki paida ki hui hai aur uski milkiyat hai. jo bhi wo karey us se puchha nahi ja sakta aur wo (uske mamlook bandey) jo karein unse puchha ja sakta hai. to unhon-ne mujh se kaha : Allah tum par raham karey ! maine jo tum se puchha sirf isi liye puchha tha taake tumhari aql ka imtihaan lun. muzena ke 2 aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap kis tarah dekhtey hain, log jo amal aaj kar rahe aur is mein mashaqqat utha rahe hain koi aisi cheez hai jiska unke barey mein faisla ho chuka aur pahley se muqaddar hai jo unmein jari ho chuki hai ya wo ab unke samney pesh ki ja rahi hai, jis tarah usey unke rasool unke paas laey hain aur un par hujjat tamam hui hai? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, balke aisi cheez hai jo unke barey mein tay ho gaee hai aur unmein jari ho chuki, aur uski tasdeeq izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki kitab mein hai : aur nafse-insani aur us zaat ki qism jisne usko theek banaya ! phir usko uski badi bhi ilhaam kar di aur neki bhi."
6740,"Alaa ke walid (Abdur-Rehman) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah insan aik lambi muddat tak ahle-jannat ke se amal karta rehta hai, phir uske liye uske amal ka khaatma ahale-jahannam ke se amal par hota hai aur bila shubah aik aadmi lamba zamana ahale-jahannam ke se amal karta rehta hai, phir uske liye uske amal ka khaatma ahle-jannat ke se amal par hota hai."
6741,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik shakhs, jis tarah wo logon ko nazar aa raha hota hai, ahle-jannat ke se amal kar raha hota hai, lekin (aakhir kaar) wo ahale-jahannam mein se hota hai aur aik aadmi, jis tarah se wo logon ko nazar aa raha hota hai ahale-jahannam ke se amal kar raha hota hai lekin (anjame-kaar) wo ahle-jannat mein se hota hai."
6742,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim, Ibrahim bin-Dinar, ibne-abi-Umar Makki aur Ahmad-bin-Abda Zabi ne hamein ibne-Uena se hadis bayan ki, alfaz ibne- Hatim aur ibne-Dinar ke hain. padhi. un donon ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan bin-Amr (bin Dinar) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Taaus se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Hazrat Adam aur Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ne (eik doosrey ko) apni apni daleelein din. Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : Adam! aap hamarey walid hain, aap ne hamein naakam kar diya aur hamein jannat se bahar nikal laey. Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : tum Musa ho, tumhen Allah Taala ne apni ham kalaami ke liye muntakhab farmaya aur apne hath se tumharey liye (apne ehkaam ko) likha, kya tum mujhey is baat par malaamat kar rahe ho jisey Allah Taala ne mere barey mein mujhey paida karne se bhi chalis (40) saal pahley muqaddar kar diya tha? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) (daleel mein) Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aa gaey, Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aa gaey. ibne-abi-Umar aur ibne- Abda ki hadis mein hai ke aik ne kaha : likha aur doosrey ne kaha : tumharey liye apne hath se Taurait likhi."
6743,"abu-Zinad ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Hazrat Adam aur Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ne aik doosrey ko dalaayel diye aur Adam (Alaihissalam) ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko daleel se haraa diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unse kaha : aap wahi Adam hain jinhoney ( khud ghalati karke apni aulad ke) logon ko ghaltiyaan karne ka rasta dikhaya aur unhein jannat se nikalwaa diya ? to Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : tumhi ho jisey Allah ne har cheez ka ilm diya aur jisey logon mein se apni risalat ke liye muntakhab farmaaya? unhon-ne kaha : haan, (to Adam (Alaihissalam) ne) farmaya : tum mujhey is baat par malaamat kar rahe ho jo mujhey paida kiye janey se bhi pahley mere muqaddar kar di gaee thi?"
6744,"Haris bin abi Zubab ne Yazeed bin Hurmuz aur Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha : ham ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Hazrat Adam aur Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ne apne rab ke samney aik doosrey ko daleelein din aur Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) daleel mein Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aa gaey, Hazrat Musa ne kaha : aap wo Adam hain jinko Allah Taala ne apne hath se paida kya, aur aap main apni Rooh ko phoonka aur aapko farishton se sajda karaya aur aapko apni jannat mein rakha, phir aap ne apni ghalati se logon ko jannat se nikalwa kar zamin mein utarwa diya? Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : tum wo Musa ho jisey Allah Taala ne apni risalat aur apni ham kalaami ke zariey se fazeelat bakhshi aur tumhen (Taurait ki) wo takhtey ata kin jin mein har cheez ki wazaahat hai aur tumhen sargoshi kiye janey wala bana kar apna qurb ata farmaya, (tum ye bataao) tumharey ilm ke mutabiq Allah ne meri paidaaish se kitni muddat pahley Taurait ko (is sura mein) likha (jis tarah wo tum par nazil huii?) Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : chalis (40) saal se (qabl.) Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : kya tum ne usmein ye ( likha hua) paya : Adam ne apne parwardigar (ke hukm ( se sartaabi ki aur raah se hat gaya? (hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ne) kaha : haan, to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum mujhey is baat par malaamat kar rahe ho ke maine wo kaam kya jo Allah ne meri paidaaish se chalis (40) saal pahley mujh par likh diya tha ke main wo kaam karunga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : is tarah Adam (Alaihissalam) ne daleel se Musa (Alaihissalam) ko laa-jawaab kar diya."
6745,"Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Hazrat Adam aur Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) ne dalaayel ka tabadla kya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : aap Adam hain jinki khata ne unhein jannat se bahar nikala? to Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ne unse kaha : kya tum Musa ho jisey Allah ne apni risalat aur ham kalaami se dusron par fazeelat di, phir tum mujhey us mamley mein malamat kar rahe ho jo meri paidaaish se pahley mere liye muqaddar kar diya gaya tha? is tarah Adam (Alaihissalam) ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko daleel se khamosh kar diya."
6746,abu-Salma aur Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un (guzishta rawiyon) ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
6747,Muhammad-bin-Sirin ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sab ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6748,"ibne-Wahab ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Haani Kholani ne abu Abdur-Rehman habli se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : Allah Taala ne aasmanon aur zamin ko paida karne se pachaas hazaar saal pahley makhlooqat ki taqdeerein tehreer farma dein thi. farmaya : aur iska arsh pani par tha."
6749,Hewa aur Naafe bin Yazeed ne abu-Haani se isi sanad ke sath usi hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki magar un donon ne ye nahi kaha : aur uska arsh pani par tha.
6750,"Hewa ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Haani ne bataya, unhon-ne abu-Abdur-Rehman habli se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna, kaha : unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : bani-Adam ke sarey dil aik dil ki sura mein Allah Taala ki ungliyon mein se do ungliyon ke darmyan hain, wo jis tarah chahta hai usey (un sab ko) ghumaata hai. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( dua kartey huey) farmaya : aey Allah ! aey dilon ko pherney waley! hamarey dilon ko apni itaat par pher de."
6751,"Amr bin Muslim ne Taaus se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bahut si sahaba ko paya wo sab ke sab ye kehtey they ke har cheez (Allah ki muqarrar karda) miqdar se hai aur maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har cheez ( Allah ki muqarrar karda ( miqdar se hai yahan tak ke (kisi kaam ko) na kar sakna aur kar sakna bhi, ya kaha : ( kisi kaam ko) kar sakna aur na kar sakna ( bhi usi miqdar se hai.)"
6752,"Muhammad-bin Ibad bin Jafar makhzumi ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mushrekeen Quraish taqdeer ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bahas karne ke liye aaey, us waqt (ye aayat ( nazil hui : jis din wo jahannam mein aundhey munh ghaseetey jaeinge , (kaha jaeyga : ( dozakh ka azab chakho , be-shak ham ne har cheez ko) tay shuda ( miqdar ke mutabiq banaya hai."
6753,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur abd bin Humaid ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Ishaq ke hain. padhi. donon ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Mamar ne ibne-Taaus se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, maine us se badh kar (Quran ke lafz ( alif-lam-mim se mushabeh (similar) koi aur cheez nahi dekhi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne ibne-Aadam par iske hissey ka zina likh diya hai, wo laa-muhaala apna hissey lega. aankh ka zina (jiska dekhna haram hai usko) dekhna hai. zaban ka zina (haram baat) kehna hai, dil tamanna rakhta hai, khahish karta hai, phir sharmgaah uski tasdeeq karti hai (aur wo zina ka irtikaab kar leta hai) ya takzeeb karti hai (aur wo iska irtikaab nahi karta.) abd ne apni riwayat mein kaha : ibne-Taaus ne apne walid se riwayat ki (kaha :) maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, (is sanad mein samaa ki sarahat hai.)"
6754,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : ibne-Aadam ke mutaalliq zina mein se iska hissey likh diya gaya hai. wo la muhaala usko hasil karne wala hai, to donon aankhen, unka zina dekhna hai aur donon kaan, unka zina sunnaa hai aur zaban, iska zina baat karna hai aur hath, iska zina pakadna hai aur paon, iska zina chal kar jana hai aur dil tamanna rakhta hai aur khahish karta hai aur sharmgaah un tamam baton ki tasdeeq karti hai (usey amalan sach kar dikhaati hai aur haram ka irtikaab ho jata hai) ya usko jhutla deti hai (haqiqi zina se bachao ho jata hai.)"
6755,"Zubaidi ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke wo kaha kartey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har paida honey wala bachcha fitrat (Allah par eman aur achai ki mohabbat) par paida hota hai, phir iske maan-baap usko yahudi, nasrani aur majusi bana detey hain, jaisey aik janwar (maan) aaza mein kaamil janwar (bachchey) ko janm deti hai, kya tumhen unmein koi uzu (khaas ang) kata hua janwar nazar aata hai? phir Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : tum chaho to ye aayat padh lo : yahi Allah ki) ata karda ( fitrat hai jis par us ne logon ki takhleeq farmai, Allah ki takhleeq mein raddo-badal nahi hota."
6756,Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : jis tarah aik (maadda) janwar bachchey ko janm deti hai. unhon-ne aaza mein kaamil zikr nahi kya.
6757,"Yunus bin Yazeed ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi paida honey wala bachcha nahi magar uski wilaadat fitrat par hoti hai. phir ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) kehtey : ye aayat padh lo : yahi Allah ki) ata karda ( fitrat hai jis par us ne logon ki takhleeq ki, Allah ki takhleeq mein tabdili nahi hogi, yahi seedha mustahkam Deen hai (jiski insani fitrat amanat daar hai.)"
6758,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi wilaadat paaney wala nahi magar wo fitrat hi par paida hua hai, phir uske waalidain usey yahudi, nasrani aur mushrik bana detey hain. aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! agar wo us se pahley mar jaaey? aap ne farmaya : Allah hi zyada jaanney wala hai ke (badey ho kar) wo bachchey kya amal karne waley they."
6759,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawia ne hadis bayan ki, neez hamein ibne-Numair ne bhi (yahi) hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, (abu-Muawia aur ibne-Numair ke walid ( donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. ibne-Numair ki hadis mein hai : koi bachcha paida honey wala bachcha nahi magar wo millat par hota hai. aur abu-Muawia se Abu-Bakar ne jo riwayat ki usmein hai : magar wo us millat (millate-Islami) par hota hai yahan tak ke uski zaban us (ke kufr ya emaan) ko bayan kar deti hai. aur abu-Muawia se abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein hai : koi wilaadat paaney wala nau-maulood nahi magar wo usi fitrat par hota hai yahan tak ke uski zaban uske (maahaul se akhaz karda) khayalat ki tarjamani karti hai."
6760,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunain, phir unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik hadis ye hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo ( bachcha ( paida hota hai, wo usi fitrat par paida hota hai, phir iske waalidain usko Yahudi aur nasrani bana detey hain jis tarah tum oonton ke bachchon ko janm dilwaatey ho. kya tum unmein se kisi ko kaan kata hua patey ho? yahan tak ke tum khud uska kaan kaat do, logon ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kya aap ne dekha ke agar wo chhota hi faut ho jaaey? farmaya : Allah hi zyada jaanney wala hai. wo (chhoti umr mein faut hone-waale bachchey) kya amal karne waley they?"
6761,Alaa ke walid Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har insan ko uski maan fitrat par janm deti hai aur uske maan-baap baad mein usko Yahudi ya nasrani ya majusi bana detey hain. agar wo donon (sahi) musalman hon to wo musalman rehta hai aur har insan ko jab uski maan janm deti hai to shaitan iske donon pahluon mein hath se maarta hai siwaey Hazrat Maryam (Alaihissalam) aur unke betey ke (unhein Allah ne us se mehfooz rakha.)
6762,"ibne-abi-Zi'ib aur Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen ki aulad ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap ne farmaya : Allah hi zyada janta hai ke) badey ho kar) wo kya amal karne waley they."
6763,"Mamar, Shuaib aur Maaqil-bin-Ubaidullah ne Zohri se Yunus aur ibne-abi-Zi'ib ki sanad ke sath un donon ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar Shuaib aur Maaqil ki hadis mein (mushrekeen ki aulad ke bajaey) mushrekeen ke chhotey bachchon ke alfaz hain."
6764,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen ke bachchon ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya, unmein se jo chhoti umr mein faut ho jayen (to unka anjam kya hoga?) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala zyada janta hai ke wo kya amal karne waley they."
6765,"Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen ke bachchon ke mutaalliq sawal kiya gaya to aap ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne jab unko paida kiya to wo zyada jaanney wala hai ke wo kya amal karne waley they."
6766,"Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis ladkey ko Hazrat khizr (Alaihissalam) ne qatl kya tha wo tabai taur par kaafir banaya gaya tha, agar wo zinda rehta to zabardasti apne maan-baap ko sarkashi aur kufr ki taraf ley jata."
6767,"Fuzel bin-Amr ne Aaisha binte-Talha se aur unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke aik bachcha faut hua to maine kaha : uske liye khush khabri ho, wo to jannat ki chidiyon mein se aik chidiyaa hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum nahi janti ke Allah Taala ne jannat ko paida kya aur dozakh ko paida kya aur uske liye bhi usmein janey waley banaey aur us ke liye bhi usmein rehney waley banaey?"
6768,"Wakee ne Talha bin Yahya se, unhon-ne apni phoophi Aaisha binte-Talha se aur unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Ansar ke aik bachchey ke janazey ke liye bulaya gaya, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! uske liye khush khabri ho ye jannat ki chidiyon mein se aik chidiya hai, us ne koi gunah kya, na gunah karne ki umr paai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya uske ilawa kuchh aur? Aaisha ! Allah Taala ne jannat mein rehney waley log paida farmaey, unhein us waqt jannat ke liye takhleeq kya jab wo apne baapon ki pushton mein they aur dozakh ke liye bhi rehney waley banaey, unhein us waqt dozakh ke liye takhleeq kya jab wo apne baapon ki pushton mein they."
6769,Ismail bin Zakariya aur Sufiyan Sory ne Talha-bin-Yahya se Wakee ki hadis ki tarah usi ki sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
6770,"Wakee ne hamein Mamar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Alqama-bin-Marsad se, unhon-ne Mugheera-bin-Abdullah-yashkari se, unhon-ne Ma'roor-bin-Suwed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye dua ki : aey Allah ! mujhey apne khawind Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne walid Hazrat Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) aur apne bhai Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) (ki zindagiyon) se mustafeed farma (fayda pahuchan) ! (Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne umaron ki aisi muddaton ka, jo muqarrar kar di gaee hain aur un dinon ka jo giney ja chukey hain aur aisey rizqon ka jo baantey ja chukey hain, sawal kiya hai. agar tum Allah se ye maangti ke tumhen aag mein diye janey waley ya qabr mein diye janey waley azab se panah ata farma de to ye zyada achchha aur zyada afzal hota. ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aap ke samney bandaron ke barey mein baat cheet hui. Misar ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhon (Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : khinzeeron ka bhi (zikr kiya gaya ke wo) maskh ho kar baney hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne maskh honey walon ki na nasl banai hai na aulad , bandar aur khinzeer us (maskh honey ke waqiey) se pahley bhi hotey they. (jo maujooda hain wo unhi ki naslein hain.)"
6771,"ibne-Bishr ne Misar se isi sanad ke sath khabar di, magar ibne-Bishr aur Wakee donon se unki (riwaayat ki hui ( hadis mein ye alfaz manqul (naqal kiye huein) hain : aag mein diye janey waley aur qabr mein diye janey waley azab se (panah maangti to behtar tha.) (ya ki bajaey aur hai.)"
6772,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein Sory ne Alqama-bin-Marsad se khabar di, unhon-ne Mugheera-bin-Abdullah-yashkari se, unhon-ne Ma'roor-bin-Suwed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne (dua kartey huey) kaha : aey Allah ! mujhey mere khawind Rasulullah (sl), mere walid Abu-Sufiyan aur mere bhai (ki daraazi Umar) se mustafeed farma ! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : tum ne Allah Taala se un muddaton ka sawal kiya hai jo muqarrar ki ja chukein aur qadmon ke un nishaanon ka jin par qadam rakhey ja chukey aur aisey rizqon ko jo taqseem kiye ja chukey. na unmein se koi cheez apna waqt aaney se pahley aa sakti hai aur na aaney ke baad muakhkhar ho sakti hai. agar tum Allah Taala se ye maangti ke wo tumhen jahannam mein diye janey waley azab aur qabr mein diye janey waley azab se bacha ley to tumharey liye behtar hota. (Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aik aadmi ne puchha : Allah ke rasool ! ye bandar aur khinzeer kya unhi mein se hain jo maskh ho kar baney they? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne kisi qaum ko halaak nahi kiya ya (farmaya :) kisi qaum ko azab nahi diya ke phir un (logon) ki nasl banaey (unke bachchey paida karke unhein aagey chalaey.) aur bila shubah bandar aur khinzeer pahley bhi maujood they. (aagey unhi ki naslein chali hain.)"
6773,"Abu-Dawud Sulaiman-bin-Mabad ne kaha : hamein-Husain-bin-Hafs ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : aur qadmon ke aisey nishan jin tak qadam pahunch chukey hain. ibne-Mabad ne kaha : un (asaatza/ustaadon) mein se kuchh ne (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman ( : iske hal honey se pahley . yani iske utarney se pahley ( wazaahati alfaz ke saath) riwayat ki."
6774,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : taqatwer momin Allah ke nazdeek kamzor momin ki nisbat behtar aur zyada mahboob hai, jabke khair donon mein (maujood) hai. jis cheez se tumhen (haqiqi) nafa pahunchey usmein hirs karo aur Allah se madad maango aur kamzor na pado (maayoos ho kar na baith) jao, agar tumhen koi (nuqsan) pahunchey to ye na kaho : kash! ! main (is tarah) karta to aisa-aisa hota, balke ye kaho : (ye ( Allah ki taqdeer hai, wo jo chahta hai karta hai, isliye ke (hasarat kartey huey) kaash! ! (kehna) shaitan ke amal (ke darwazey) ko khol deta hai."
